":"Question","name":"Can I create a favicon from text?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Use the text favicon generator to create a favicon from letters, initials, a short word, Unicode characters, or emoji. Choose the font, colors, and background shape before downloading the favicon package."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many letters should a text favicon use?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"One or two letters usually work best because favicons are displayed at small sizes in browser tabs and bookmarks. Short initials are easier to read than longer words."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What files does the text favicon generator download?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The download includes favicon.ico, PNG favicon sizes, Apple Touch Icon, Android icons, and a web manifest file for a complete modern favicon setup."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I make a transparent text favicon?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Type transparent into the background color field to create a text favicon without a solid background color."}}]}</script><noscript data-vue-tag="ssr"><style>.g-image--loading{display:none;}</style></noscript>
